reviewText:
//WARNING//  I'll illuminate this up front, because the store page does not.  This is only 'Part one' of a three part game.  At the time of writing (31/5/14) there is no mention of when the other parts are coming out or whether this purchase is for all of them or just the first one.  This is either bad communication or far worse sneaky scamming on the part of the publishers.

That out of the way, my recommendation proceeds objectively.

Clunky but interesting indy title.  Largely a point and click adventure game with brief (and superficial) shooting sections.  Acceptable graphics/sound and good performance, poor controls but not enough to hurt it too badly.  It's the interesting and compelling ideas and themes that it plays with that brings it up to the level of recommended; just.
